n我唔知呢度有幾多人會理乜野叫art direction，如果你想影人像，其實有好多你用相機/vsco控制唔到既野都好緊要，造型/姿勢/model/地點/氣氛之類，睇相唔係剩係睇人張相點影d色點tune架，比你用佢部機，抄埋佢d preset都無用<br />\n<br />\n我是但搵d例子，都已經好多唔同style：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/kelsography/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fkelsography%2F&d=k3FtystjW27N0V0sEM17sjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=9ac61548\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/kelsography/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/analogueportraits/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fanalogueportraits%2F&d=k3FtystjW27N0V0sEM17sjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=98b3a1ac\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/analogueportraits/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/subjectivelyobjective/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fsubjectivelyobjective%2F&d=k3FtystjW27N0V0sEM17sjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=c26f759f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/subjectivelyobjective/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/noicemag/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fnoicemag%2F&d=k3FtystjW27N0V0sEM17sjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=4779fd0e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/noicemag/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/silvia.grazioli/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fsilvia.grazioli%2F&d=k3FtystjW27N0V0sEM17sjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=eecbcdf3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/silvia.grazioli/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/explore/tags/rentalmag/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fexplore%2Ftags%2Frentalmag%2F&d=k3FtystjW27N0V0sEM17sjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=f13365ce\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/explore/tags/rentalmag/</a>"},{"pid":"214c86550b407570d39c889fc569e65a4bd6d6ed","tid":537232,"uid":167755,"like":1,"dislike":0,"scor